      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 49,
      "text": "Correct me, I'm wrong but we're currently getting data for all of our like comps listed for our properties in the platform right now and that's what's coming over."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 175.19,
      "start_time": 167.89,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 50,
      "text": "Um What we were trying to scope out and figure out if it's even possible, it's just getting that same data, but on a broader spectrum."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 181.63,
      "start_time": 175.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 51,
      "text": "Um I don't know exactly how broad I think it just determined be like determined by like pricing and what you guys can actually do."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 192.96,
      "start_time": 181.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 52,
      "text": "But obviously like we would be at a minimum like the hope would be like, we could figure out a few target markets that we have that, like, maybe it's, you know, 5678 markets or something like that."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 197.49,
      "start_time": 192.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 53,
      "text": "And then we go for like, you know, like you said, like, kind of some parameters, right?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 209.76,
      "start_time": 197.5,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 54,
      "text": "We don't need every single thing, but maybe any property, it's over 100 units that's in this age band range that's, you know, not affordable or, you know, whatever like parameters you guys have."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 218.67,
      "start_time": 209.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 55,
      "text": "Um We'd be open to all that to like filtering down to like a, a good set of data um that we think is, you know, needed or useful."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 224.58,
      "start_time": 218.68,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 56,
      "text": "Um But I guess what we don't know is just, you know, from your perspective, is that possible?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 226.32,
      "start_time": 224.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 57,
      "text": "What's something like that gonna cost?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 226.63,
      "start_time": 226.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 58,
      "text": "Uh"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 228.56,
      "start_time": 228.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 59,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 231.12,
      "start_time": 228.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 60,
      "text": "Uh Short answer is it's, it's certainly possible."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 239.47,
      "start_time": 231.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 61,
      "text": "Uh It's not really like an out of the box solution but uh for particular partners, we've, we've had conversations around this and we, we've set this up."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 248.6,
      "start_time": 239.74,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 62,
      "text": "Um I guess the next question I, I know in the last time, uh me and me and cole connected, it was the interest was around historicals versus ongoing."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 249.91,
      "start_time": 248.61,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 63,
      "text": "Uh Is that still the case?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 256.71,
      "start_time": 249.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 64,
      "text": "Like, are you looking for a uh historical dump of this data like a one time thing or is it something you want to be uh ongoing as well?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 268.03,
      "start_time": 259.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 65,
      "text": "Uh It would be a hope for history and then like an ongoing and again, these are just like best case scenarios, right?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 276.18,
      "start_time": 268.04,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 66,
      "text": "Like we're not, we understand that there's just, you know, we're kind of just theory wanting to jump on a call and theorize about it a little bit, but that, that would be what we wanna do."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 277.04,
      "start_time": 276.58,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 67,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 280.2,
      "start_time": 277.21,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 68,
      "text": "Uh, we, we would just do it the same, same way effectively."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 289.71,
      "start_time": 280.21,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 69,
      "text": "Like, it's, it's pretty easy for us to set up just for, I guess your knowledge um IQ as a whole has uh we're up to 21 million units in 85,000 properties."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 299.88,
      "start_time": 290.29,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 70,
      "text": "So if you look at like what uh S two is uh currently ingesting the data feed, it's about 500 properties and 100 and 50,000 units of that competitive data."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 310.7,
      "start_time": 300.6,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 71,
      "text": "Um If you take like Dallas Fort Worth, for example, uh we have about 15 1500 properties there in uh almost a half a million units."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 321.48,
      "start_time": 311.62,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 72,
      "text": "So it really does become just like a uh a budget and pricing conversation in terms of like the feasibility and the uh uh tech side of, of giving you that data."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 323.04,
      "start_time": 321.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 73,
      "text": "It's relatively easy for us to do."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 325.45,
      "start_time": 323.88,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 74,
      "text": "Ok, cool."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 331.06,
      "start_time": 325.62,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 75,
      "text": "So um the, the question really just becomes then like the parameters and then, then how we price this out."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 338.18,
      "start_time": 331.07,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 76,
      "text": "Um For instance, we, we price this out with uh lo local Dallas providers and it was around like a five grand incremental."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 346.86,
      "start_time": 338.19,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 77,
      "text": "Uh We price this out with um larger national partners for 20 plus markets and that was in the range of like, you know, 30 grand in incremental from what they were doing."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 352.34,
      "start_time": 347.26,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 78,
      "text": "Um, and then we've had some institutional conversations as well for, for full, uh, for full database."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 356.08,
      "start_time": 353.33,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 79,
      "text": "It's a large range of what we can do."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 356.74,
      "start_time": 356.62,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 80,
      "text": "Uh,"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 368.28,
      "start_time": 356.75,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 81,
      "text": "yeah, I mean, I think, I think we'd love to talk about full database but, um, I, I, you know, it just depends on what you guys are able to do and, you know, if we can strike a deal on price and things like that."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 370.18,
      "start_time": 368.29,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 82,
      "text": "But um we, we'd love, it"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 371.55,
      "start_time": 370.97,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 83,
      "text": "sounds good."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 381.87,
      "start_time": 371.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 84,
      "text": "And then in terms of the historicals, um Cole will find the shore that we, we have introduced that or we will be introducing that uh in the uh um uh app experience."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 389.35,
      "start_time": 382.09,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 85,
      "text": "Um And then in terms of the data dump for that, uh we just require a, a uh you know, several year contract because in that case, it's like a one time thing."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 394.48,
      "start_time": 389.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 86,
      "text": "Like once you have the data, you, you have that sure understand ongoing is much easier."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 398.43,
      "start_time": 394.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 87,
      "text": "Like I can just uh go back to our finance team and price out some scenarios."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 409.46,
      "start_time": 398.44,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 88,
      "text": "I've got the nine markets that were previously sent which were um Dallas Houston, Atlanta, Phoenix, Orlando, Jupiter, Florida, Raleigh Durham and Charlotte."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 414.6,
      "start_time": 409.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 89,
      "text": "Is there anything additional you want me to price out like outside of full market uh or full national?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 421.54,
      "start_time": 415.54,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 90,
      "text": "No, I mean, those would be like the, I think main markets, but we only got those for our comps."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 421.82,
      "start_time": 421.55,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 91,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 426.42,
      "start_time": 421.83,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 92,
      "text": "Like, um, but I don't think we got, like, the broad market for all those, um,"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 427.39,
      "start_time": 426.43,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 93,
      "text": "currently."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 427.91,
      "start_time": 427.4,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 94,
      "text": "That's right."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 427.94,
      "start_time": 427.92,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 95,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 428.76,
      "start_time": 428.22,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 96,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 437.36,
      "start_time": 428.77,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 97,
      "text": "Um, but yeah, outside of, like, getting, like, national or getting into, like, you know, just, uh, yes, that's accurate."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 449.56,
      "start_time": 438.76,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 98,
      "text": "The easiest way to do this is almost like, give you rates for, uh, certain, like, uh, unit bands, almost like data thresholds that you can get up to and then we can piece the markets into that."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 451.7,
      "start_time": 449.57,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 99,
      "text": "If that makes sense, that's totally fine."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 462.31,
      "start_time": 452,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 100,
      "text": "So, right, it's like here's that at the largest scale, here's would be at, at the smallest scale, here's we'd be at, here's the rates for those and then let's work into that and apply filter you would get to, to where you need to get at."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 467.89,
      "start_time": 462.66,
      "recording_attendee_id": "d904f465-0692-4e6f-ab64-8a3318b668ee",
      "order_number": 101,
      "text": "And as far as database, like constraints like historical wise, uh How far back do you guys go again?"
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 472,
      "start_time": 468.12,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 102,
      "text": "So we have um uh the data goes back to October 2020."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 475.28,
      "start_time": 472.17,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 103,
      "text": "Uh There is some data Degra degradation."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 482.74,
      "start_time": 475.29,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 104,
      "text": "So, um if you go back a year, we've got like 90% coverage of that um uh 21 million unit database."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
      "end_time": 489.56,
      "start_time": 483.13,
      "recording_attendee_id": "49941232-e6e4-464e-a0a5-cc784311db05",
      "order_number": 105,
      "text": "If you go back two years, that drops to like 63 years, it's like 35% because the database has been growing as the company has been growing."
    },
    {
      "id": "431d35fa-1e0c-4891-bbf6-a27242a5516e",
      "recording_id": "57f6eb47-7442-4402-9421-90fc11bad451",
